title: 20 PCS BBQ Metal Skewers Stainless Steel,7.87''/20cm Reusable Kebab Skewers for Grilling, Oven, and BBQ
features: 1. Durable Material: DAJING skewers stainless steel are crafted from high-quality Type 440 STAINLESS STEEL, offering superior corrosion and abrasion resistance. All edges are polished for safe use, unlike traditional bamboo or wooden sticks which can break or burn.

2. Reusable: These metal skewers for grilling are reusable, making them an eco-friendly choice. They do not break or burn, and their 7.87-inch length is perfect for holding a large amount of food, ideal for small picnics or sharing with friends and family.

3. Perfect Use: Enjoy versatile cooking with DAJING kebab skewers. Use them in the oven, on a kebab machine, or at a BBQ to prepare delicious dishes like Turkish shish kebabs, adana kebabs, kofte, and more. Perfect for any occasion, from BBQ parties to Christmas celebrations.

4. Easy To Clean: The smooth surface of our stainless steel skewers ensures that food residue won't stick, making cleaning a breeze. Simply wash with warm water, mild detergent, and air dry for easy maintenance.

5. Attentive Service: Your safety is our priority. Please use these sharp-tipped skewers carefully and wear safety gloves to prevent hand injuries. If you have any questions or need assistance, our dedicated support team is here to help.
